    "body": "This is a performance issue. The MessageView is a heavy component and 80% of the scroll time is spent on creating the MesageView. The experience is much better if we use ListView.reuseItems, but it it available in 5.15. Even with reuseItems there are still small hiccups that needs to be investigated.\r\n\r\nThe proposed solution is to enable ListView.reuseItems (after #8642 is completed) and further investigate the smaller hiccups. ",
